7e75/66ab3391df09cccbbf980dcd_surveillance-monitors-screens-group.webp" alt="top signage software in india" class="image-sml"/></div><div class="feature-heading"><strong>Screens</strong></div><p class="paragraph-2-w">The goal is to assign each screen a unique identifier. A screen is a device that displays content via a digital signage player application.</p></a><a data-w-tab="Tab 3" class="tab-on w-inline-block w-tab-link"><div class="colour-block-sml-3"><img width="15" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66a23afd8c7660b4882c7e75/66ab3561ae90877588edf903_rocket.webp" alt="top free signage software" class="image-sml"/></div><div class="feature-heading"><strong>Payloads</strong></div><p class="paragraph-2-w">The purpose of the payload is to deliver content from the console to the client application. A payload consists of a set of images or videos that will be played in digital signage display.</p></a></div><div class="w-tab-content"><div data-w-tab="Tab 1" class="w-tab-pane w--tab-active"><img sizes="(max-width: 767px) 90vw, (max-width: 991px) 72vw, (max-width: 1279px) 47vw, 550px" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66a23afd8c7660b4882c7e75/66ab45f4cab244f0b0f1a2a3_groups-p-500.webp 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66a23afd8c7660b4882c7e75/66ab45f4cab244f0b0f1a2a3_groups-p-800.webp 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66a23afd8c7660b4882c7e75/66ab45f4cab244f0b0f1a2a3_groups.webp 1080w" alt="Digital Signage Player" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66a23afd8c7660b4882c7e75/66ab45f4cab244f0b0f1a2a3_groups.webp" class="phone"/></div><div data-w-tab="Tab 2" class="w-tab-pane"><img sizes="(max-width: 767px) 90vw, (max-width: 991px) 72vw, (max-width: 1279px) 47vw, 550px" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66a23afd8c7660b4882c7e75/66ab4627177d7cf5a6e3401b_screens-p-500.webp 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66a23afd8c7660b4882c7e75/66ab4627177d7cf5a6e3401b_screens-p-800.webp 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66a23afd8c7660b