---brix"></div></div></div></div><div style="height:0px;-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0.9, 0.9, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0.9, 0.9, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0.9, 0.9, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0.9, 0.9, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0" class="accordion-content---brix"><p class="accordion-paragraph---brix">As of August 2024, Signager digital signage system is compatible with Android TV and Android AOSP operating systems. The Signager team is actively developing &quot;Signager Client&quot; applications for additional operating systems, including WebOS, Tizen OS, and Windows.</p></div></section><div data-w-id="301c3066-ea06-fb98-2426-48aac3e108a5" style="border-color:rgba(0,0,0,0)" class="accordion-item---brix accordion-1---brix"><div class="accordion-trigger---brix"><div class="accordion-item-title---brix">Is The Signager - Digital Signage Solution Available For All Users?</div><div style="background-color:rgb(255,255,255)" class="accordion-arrow-wrap---brix"><div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(90deg) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(90deg) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(90deg) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(90deg) skew(0, 0)" class="accordion-arrow-wrapper---brix"><div class="arrow-line---brix _2---brix"></div><div class="arrow-line---brix _1---brix"></div></div></div></div><div style="height:0px;-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0.9, 0.9, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0.9, 0.9, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0.9, 0.9, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0.9, 0.9, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0" class="accordion-content---brix"><p class="accordion-paragraph---brix">Signager is currently in the beta development stage and is available only to select users. If you are interested in testing Signager digital signage player, please <a href="https://www.signager.cloud/host/register.html">register</a> and request account activation.<br/><br/>If your request is not immediately honored, you will eventually receive an email following the global rollout with a pre-activated account.</p></div></div><div data-w-id="301c3066-ea06-fb98-2426-48aac3e108b3" style="border-color:rgba(0,0,0,0)" class="accordion-item---brix accordion-1---brix"><div class="accordion-trigger---brix"><div class="accordion-item-title---brix">What Is The Anticipated Pricing For The Signager - Digital Signage Solutions?</div><div style="background-color:rgb(255,255,255)" class="accordion-arrow-wrap---brix"><div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(90deg) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(90deg) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(90deg) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(90deg) skew(0, 0)" class="accordion-arrow-wrapper---brix"><div class="arrow-line---brix _2---brix"></div><div class="arrow-line---brix _1---brix"></div></div></div></div><div style="height:0px;-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0.9, 0.9, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0.9, 0.9, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0.9, 0.9, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0.9, 0.9, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0" class="accordion-content---brix"><p class="accordion-paragraph---brix">Firstly, the pricing for Signager will be significantly more affordable compared to current digital signage softwares available online.<br/><br/>The cost of Signager will vary based on the features bundled with the system. However, there will always be a FREE VERSION available, which supports an unlimited number of screens with certain feature limitations.</p></div></div><div data-w-id="301c3066-ea06-fb98-2426-48aac3e108c2" style="border-color:rgba(0,0,0,0)" class="accordion-item---brix accordion-1---brix"><div class="accordion-trigger---brix"><div class="accordion-item-title---brix">Can Signager Be Downloaded And Operated On A Local System?</div><div style="background-color:rgb(255,255,255)" class="accordion-arrow-wrap---brix"><div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(90deg) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(90deg) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(90deg) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(90deg) skew(0, 0)" class="accordion-arrow-wrapper---brix"><div class="arrow-line---brix _2---brix"></div><div class="arrow-line---brix _1---brix"></div></div></div></div><div style="height:0px;-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0.9, 0.9, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0.9, 0.9, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0.9, 0.9, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0.9, 0.9, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0" class="accordion-content---brix"><p class="accordion-paragraph---brix">Signager <em>Digital Signage Software</em> is hosted on a dedicated cloud server, ensuring easy and secure access from anywhere in the world for controlling the client application.<br/><br/>While the host software cannot be downloaded, the client application can be downloaded and installed on various digital signage display devices. It can then be authenticated to play content from the payloads.<br/></p></div></div></div></div><script src="https://d3e54v103j8qbb.cloudfront.net/js/jquery-3.5.1.min.dc5e7f18c8.js?site=66a23afd8c7660b4882c7e75" type="text/javascript" integrity="sha256-9/aliU8dGd2tb6OSsuzixeV4y/faTqgFtohetphbbj0=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script><script src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66a23afd8c7660b4882c7e75/js/webflow.76cf99f4f.js" type="text/javascript"></script></body></html>